# N1 - Array Exercises

Base exercises focused on:

- array traversal
- index manipulation
- searching
- counting
- reversing
- frequency
- shifting elements
- logical reasoning

## Goals

- strengthen problem solving
- improve array manipulation
- practice algorithmic thinking
- build strong programming fundamentals

## Rules

Most exercises avoid:
- Stream API
- Collections
- Set / Map
- utility methods

Focus:
- loops
- conditions
- manual manipulation
- clean logic

## Topics

- linear search
- counting occurrences
- biggest/smallest number
- reverse array
- move zeros
- rotation
- duplicates
- frequency
- two pointers